-- Louis-Dreyfus Family Forms Russian Farming Venture With Sistema
-- B y   Y u l i y a   F e d o r i n o v a
-- 2012-04-04T12:47:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-04/louis-dreyfus-family-forms-russian-farming-venture-with-sistema.html
Louis-Dreyfus family members formed
a farming joint venture in  Russia  with AFK Sistema, billionaire
Vladimir Evtushenkov’s holding company, Sistema said in a
statement today.  The venture, called RZ Agro Holding Ltd., will grow grain
and oilseeds on 87,500 hectares of land in the Rostov region of
southern Russia, according to the statement.  “We are firm believers in the success of RZ Agro
Holding”, said Gérard Louis-Dreyfus and Peter Mann, the
representatives of the family shareholders involved in the
venture.  To contact the reporter on this story:
